00:22:29.483 --> 00:22:32.528 line:90% position:50% align:center
You could say our work now
is like a warm-up, isn’t it?

00:22:32.528 --> 00:22:36.699 line:90% position:50% align:center
It’s a warm-up
for that greatest teaching campaign

00:22:36.699 --> 00:22:40.453 line:90% position:50% align:center
that is just around the corner.

00:22:40.453 --> 00:22:44.457 line:90% position:50% align:center
So please continue to observe carefully

00:22:44.457 --> 00:22:46.417 line:90% position:50% align:center
