00:22:46.417 --> 00:22:49.128 line:90% position:50% align:center
and you learned a lot about that in school,
no doubt about it.

00:22:49.128 --> 00:22:51.380 line:90% position:50% align:center
And may Jehovah continue

00:22:51.380 --> 00:22:56.260 line:90% position:50% align:center
to bless you most beloved
Gilead students, almost graduates.

00:22:56.260 --> 00:22:59.764 line:90% position:50% align:center
May he bless you as you apply

00:22:59.764 --> 00:23:03.518 line:90% position:50% align:center
all the wonderful things
you’ve learned during this school,

00:23:03.518 --> 00:23:06.146 line:90% position:50% align:center
and that includes learning

00:23:06.146 --> 00:23:09.190 line:90% position:50% align:center
to imitate the Great Teacher.

00:23:12.319 --> 00:23:15.405 line:90% position:50% align:center
Well, we sincerely thank you, Brother Lett,

00:23:15.405 --> 00:23:19.910 line:90% position:50% align:center
